  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Natural Tones\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Natural Tones\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#FAF8F5] text-[#3D3B38] font-sans flex flex-col p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#D9826C] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <svg width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"white\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 2L14.5 9H21L16 13L17.5 20L12 16L6.5 20L8 13L3 9H9.5L12 2Z\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif;\\\">CoralNomad</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84] font-medium\\\">v2.4 Naturalist Edition</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#E5E0D8] bg-white\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Split -->\\n  <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 flex-1 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- Left: Upload Panel -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#E5E0D8] flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-medium mb-2\\\">Upload Specimens</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84] mb-6\\\">Drop your high-res coral photography here. Supported formats: RAW, JPG, PNG.</p>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 border-2 border-dashed border-[#D9D1C5] rounded-[24px] bg-[#FCFAF7] flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-[#E8D5C4] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\\\">\\n            <svg width=\\\"32\\\" height=\\\"32\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#8E8A84\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\"><path d=\\\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\\\"/><polyline points=\\\"17 8 12 3 7 8\\\"/><line x1=\\\"12\\\" y1=\\\"3\\\" x2=\\\"12\\\" y2=\\\"15\\\"/></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#4A7C7A]\\\">Select Multiple Photos</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#BAB4AD] mt-1\\\">or drag and drop</span>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-6\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[#8E8A84]\\\">\\n            <span>Queue</span>\\n            <span>8 Files</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 bg-[#E5E0D8] rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#4A7C7A] w-3/4\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#4A7C7A] italic\\\">Analyzing pigmentation and skeletal structure...</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right: Identification & Preview Grid -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#E5E0D8] flex-1 flex flex-col min-h-0\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-6\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-medium\\\">Generated Identifications</h2>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Specimens successfully cataloged with vision AI.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-[#F5F2EE] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Re-Scan</button>\\n            <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-[#D9826C] text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-md shadow-[#D9826C]/20\\\">Export to Excel</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Scrollable Grid Area (Visual Only) -->\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 overflow-hidden flex-1\\\">\\n          <!-- Item 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#E5E0D8] rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Specimen A</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Acropora Cervicornis</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Golden Staghorn\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Item 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#D9826C]/10 rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#D9826C]\\\">Specimen B</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Diploria Labyrinthiformis</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Azure Maze Brain\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Item 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#4A7C7A]/10 rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#4A7C7A]\\\">Specimen C</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Montastraea Cavernosa</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Starry Grotto\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Item 4 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#E8D5C4] rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Specimen D</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Pocillopora Damicornis</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Rose Cauliflower\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Excel Preview Indicator -->\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-6 bg-[#FCFAF7] border border-[#E5E0D8] rounded-2xl p-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-[#217346]/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n              <svg width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"#217346\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><path d=\\\"M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm2 16h-8v-2h8v2zm0-4h-8v-2h8v2zm-3-5V3.5L18.5 9H13z\\\"/></svg>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">coral_analysis_export_2023.xlsx</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#BAB4AD]\\\">Includes high-res thumbnails and GPS metadata embeddings.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold bg-[#4A7C7A]/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-full\\\">Ready to download</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- Bottom Micro-Nav -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[11px] text-[#BAB4AD] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-8\\\">\\n      <span>Marine AI Core</span>\\n      <span>Taxonomy Cloud</span>\\n      <span>Ethical Data Sourcing</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div>\302\251 2024 Biosphere Systems</div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Natural Tones\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Natural Tones\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#FAF8F5] text-[#3D3B38] font-sans flex flex-col p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-8\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#D9826C] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <svg width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"white\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 2L14.5 9H21L16 13L17.5 20L12 16L6.5 20L8 13L3 9H9.5L12 2Z\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif;\\\">CoralNomad</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84] font-medium\\\">v2.4 Naturalist Edition</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#E5E0D8] bg-white\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Split -->\\n  <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 flex-1 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- Left: Upload Panel -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#E5E0D8] flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-medium mb-2\\\">Upload Specimens</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84] mb-6\\\">Drop your high-res coral photography here. Supported formats: RAW, JPG, PNG.</p>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 border-2 border-dashed border-[#D9D1C5] rounded-[24px] bg-[#FCFAF7] flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-[#E8D5C4] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\\\">\\n            <svg width=\\\"32\\\" height=\\\"32\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"#8E8A84\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\"><path d=\\\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\\\"/><polyline points=\\\"17 8 12 3 7 8\\\"/><line x1=\\\"12\\\" y1=\\\"3\\\" x2=\\\"12\\\" y2=\\\"15\\\"/></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#4A7C7A]\\\">Select Multiple Photos</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#BAB4AD] mt-1\\\">or drag and drop</span>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-6\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[#8E8A84]\\\">\\n            <span>Queue</span>\\n            <span>8 Files</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-1 bg-[#E5E0D8] rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#4A7C7A] w-3/4\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#4A7C7A] italic\\\">Analyzing pigmentation and skeletal structure...</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right: Identification & Preview Grid -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#E5E0D8] flex-1 flex flex-col min-h-0\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-6\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-medium\\\">Generated Identifications</h2>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Specimens successfully cataloged with vision AI.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-[#F5F2EE] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Re-Scan</button>\\n            <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-[#D9826C] text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-md shadow-[#D9826C]/20\\\">Export to Excel</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Scrollable Grid Area (Visual Only) -->\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 overflow-hidden flex-1\\\">\\n          <!-- Item 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#E5E0D8] rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#8E8A84]\\\">Specimen A</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Acropora Cervicornis</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Golden Staghorn\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Item 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#D9826C]/10 rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#D9826C]\\\">Specimen B</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Diploria Labyrinthiformis</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8E8A84] mt-2 italic\\\">\\\"Azure Maze Brain\\\"</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <!-- Item 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 rounded-[20px] bg-[#FAF8F5] border border-[#F0EDE9] flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#4A7C7A]/10 rounded-[16px] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[#4A7C7A]\\\">Specimen C</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#4A7C7A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Scientific Name</span>\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium text-[#3D3B38]\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Georgia\', serif; font-style: italic;\\\">Montastraea Cavernosa</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-xs t