    thinking: "**Confirming Successful Compilation**\n\nI\'ve got good news! Everything is compiling without a hitch, so that part of the process is complete. I\'m feeling confident about crafting the final concise summary. The focus will be on professionalism and helpfulness, and I\'ll stick to the specific guidelines.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "Kullan\304\261c\304\261 talebiniz do\304\237rultusunda, uygulamadaki di\304\237er t\303\274m alanlar kald\304\261r\304\261lm\304\261\305\237 ve **yaln\304\261zca \"Suggested Trade Name\" (\303\226nerilen Ticari Ad)** alan\304\261 b\304\261rak\304\261lm\304\261\305\237t\304\261r. Yap\304\261lan g\303\274ncellemeler a\305\237a\304\237\304\261da \303\266zetlenmi\305\237tir:\n\n- **Sadele\305\237tirilmi\305\237 Aray\303\274z**: Mercan foto\304\237raflar\304\261n\304\261 inceledi\304\237iniz ve d\303\274zenledi\304\237iniz ekrandaki bilimsel s\304\261n\304\261fland\304\261rma, bak\304\261m seviyesi, \304\261\305\237\304\261k, ak\304\261nt\304\261, konumland\304\261rma ve fiziksel a\303\247\304\261klama gibi t\303\274m karma\305\237\304\261k giri\305\237 alanlar\304\261 kald\304\261r\304\261lm\304\261\305\237t\304\261r. Art\304\261k sadece y\303\274klenen foto\304\237raf\304\261n dosya ad\304\261 ve yan\304\261ndaki geni\305\237letilmi\305\237 **Suggested Trade Name** alan\304\261 g\303\266r\303\274nmektedir.\n- **Yal\304\261nla\305\237t\304\261r\304\261lm\304\261\305\237 Gemini Analizi**: Arka plandaki yapay zekaya g\303\266nderilen sorgu ve veri \305\237emas\304\261 optimize edilmi\305\237tir. Model art\304\261k g\303\266rselleri analiz ederken yaln\304\261zca yarat\304\261c\304\261, canl\304\261 ve \303\247ekici ticari ad \303\266nerileri \303\274retmektedir.\n- **Hafifletilmi\305\237 Excel \303\207\304\261kt\304\261s\304\261**: D\304\261\305\237a aktarma mekanizmas\304\261 g\303\274ncellenerek gereksiz s\303\274tunlar temizlenmi\305\237tir. \304\260ndirdi\304\237iniz Excel dosyas\304\261nda yaln\304\261zca **Coral Photo** (Mercan Foto\304\237raf\304\261) ve **Suggested Trade Name** (\303\226nerilen Ticari Ad) s\303\274tunlar\304\261 bulunmaktad\304\261r. S\303\274tun geni\305\237likleri ve h\303\274cre y\303\274kseklikleri bu iki veriye g\303\266re m\303\274kemmel \305\237ekilde hizalanm\304\261\305\237t\304\261r.\n- **Modern G\303\266rsel Tema