  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Assessing the Inquiry**\n\nI\'m currently dissecting the user\'s Turkish query regarding API costs. I\'m focusing on the specifics of analyzing 300 photos and translating this into a cost estimate. The user\'s question, \"ne kadar maliyet oluyor? 300 adet foto\304\237raf incelemesi ortalama ne kadar tutacakt\304\261r?\" is the core of my analysis.\n\n\n**Determining Informational Depth**\n\nI\'ve determined this is a purely informational request, requiring a conceptual explanation in Turkish. I\'ll maintain a simple, user-friendly tone, avoiding jargon. My focus is now calculating the cost of processing 300 photos by identifying and pricing Gemini API options, specifically the Flash models to fit this use case and query type.\n\n\n**Calculating Token Costs**\n\nI\'ve completed the token cost calculations for the photo analysis. For 300 photos at standard resolution, the total input tokens are approximately 107,400, costing roughly $0.008055. Output tokens total 9,000, costing $0.0027. Even with a more conservative estimate of 2000 tokens per image and 100 output tokens, the costs remain very low.\n\n\n**Estimating Potential Costs**\n\nI\'ve refined the cost analysis, accounting for a more generous token estimate per image. Even with this, the cost remains under $0.10 for 300 photos using the Gemini 1.5 Flash model. I also discovered the free tier offered by Google AI Studio, which could mean the processing is completely free for the user, depending on usage.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "**Gemini 3.5 Flash** (ve 1.5 Flash) modelinin maliyetleri son derece d\303\274\305\237\303\274kt\303\274r. 300 adet foto\304\237raf\304\261 analiz etmenin ortalama maliyet tablosu \305\237u \305\237ekildedir:\n\n### 1. \303\234cretsiz S\303\274r\303\274m (Google AI Studio Free Tier)\nGoogle AI Studio\'nun sundu\304\237u varsay\304\261lan API anahtar\304\261 ile bu i\305\237lem **tamamen \303\274cretsizdir ($0.00)**. \n* **G\303\274nl\303\274k Limit:** G\303\274nl\303\274k 1.500 istek hakk\304\261 vard\304\261r.\n* **Dakikal\304\261k Limit:** Dakikada 15 istek s\304\261n\304\261r\304\261 bulunur.\n* *Not:* Uygulamada thundering-herd ve hata limitlerini \303\266nlemek i\303\247in geli\305\237tirdi\304\237imiz **s\304\261ral\304\261 (sequential) i\305\237leme ve otomatik hata tekrar deneme mekanizmas\304\261** sayesinde 300 adet foto\304\237raf\304\261 dakikal\304\261k limitleri a\305\237mayacak \305\237ekilde zamana yayarak tamamen \303\274cretsiz analiz edebilirsiniz.\n\n---\n\n### 2. \303\234cretli S\303\274r\303\274m (Pay-as-you-go / Kulland\304\261k\303\247a \303\226de)\nE\304\237er kendi faturaland\304\261r\304\261lm\304\261\305\237 Google Cloud projenizi ba\304\237lay\304\261p \303\274cretli katmana ge\303\247i\305\237 yaparsan\304\261z, modelin fiyatland\304\261rmas\304\261 milyonda bir token (1M tokens) \303\274zerinden yap\304\261l\304\261r:\n\n* **Giri\305\237 (Input) \303\234creti:** Milyon token ba\305\237\304\261na **$0.075**\n* **\303\207\304\261k\304\261\305\237 (Output) \303\234creti:** Milyon token ba\305\237\304\261na **$0.30**\n\n#### 300 Foto\304\237raf \304\260\303\247in Detayl\304\261 Hesaplama:\n1. **Foto\304\237raf Ba\305\237\304\261na Giri\305\237 Token\304\261:** Gemini modellerinde her standart g\303\266rsel ortalama **258 token** olarak hesaplan\304\261r. Yan\304\261ndaki metin istemiyle birlikte g\303\266rsel ba\305\237\304\261na yakla\305\237\304\261k 300 giri\305\237 token\304\261 harcan\304\261r.\n   * *300 G\303\266rsel \303\227 300 Token = 90,000 Giri\305\237 Token\304\261* $\\rightarrow$ **Maliyet: ~$0.0067** (1 sentten az)\n2. **Foto\304\237raf Ba\305\237\304\261na \303\207\304\261k\304\261\305\237 Token\304\261:** Sadece \"Suggested Trade Name\" (\303\226nerilen Ticari \304\260sim) d\303\266nd\303\274rd\303\274\304\237\303\274m\303\274z i\303\247in yan\304\261tlar \303\247ok k\304\261sad\304\261r (ortalama 10-15 token).\n   * *300 Yan\304\261t \303\227 15 Token = 4,500 \303\207\304\261k\304\261\305\237 Token\304\261* $\\rightarrow$ **Maliyet: ~$0.0013**\n\n**\303\226zetle 300 Foto\304\237raf\304\261n Toplam \303\234cretli Maliyeti:** Ortalama **$0.01 (yakla\305\237\304\261k 35-40 kuru\305\237)** tutacakt\304\261r. En y\303\274ksek \303\247\303\266z\303\274n\303\274rl\303\274kl\303\274 detay taramalar\304\261nda bile bu maliyet **$0.05\'\304\261 (yakla\305\237\304\261k 1.70 TL)** asla ge\303\247meyecektir.\n\n---\n\n### \303\226neriler ve H\304\261z \304\260pu\303\247lar\304\261:\n* **\303\207\303\266z\303\274n\303\274rl\303\274k:** Foto\304\237raflar\304\261 y\303\274klemeden \303\266nce boyutlar\304\261n\304\261 optimize etmek (\303\266rne\304\237in 800x800 piksele d\303\274\305\237\303\274rmek) hem y\303\274kleme h\304\261z\304\261n\304\261 ciddi oranda art\304\261r\304\261r hem de veri aktar\304\261m\304\261n\304\261 kolayla\305\237t\304\261r\304\261r. Modelin isimlendirme ba\305\237ar\304\261s\304\261n\304\261 etkilemez.\n* **S\304\261ral\304\261 \304\260\305\237leme:** Sunucu taraf\304\261na ekledi\304\237imiz s\304\261ral\304\261 istek i\305\237leme yap\304\261s\304\261 sayesinde, 300 foto\304\237raf\304\261 tek seferde y\303\274kleseniz dahi taray\304\261c\304\261n\304\261z veya API ba\304\237lant\304\261n\304\261z a\305\237\304\261r\304\261 y\303\274kten dolay\304\261 yar\304\261da kesilmeden g\303\274venli bir \305\237ekilde s\304\261rayla tamamlan\304\261p Excel\'e d\303\266n\303\274\305\237t\303\274r\303\274lecektir."
